(      1,000     2,000 )
(      2,000     1,000 )

Coefficients matrix determinant:
|      1,000     2,000 |
|      2,000     1,000 | =     -3,000

Triangle matrix:
(      1,000     2,000    10,000 )
(      0,000    -3,000    -7,500 )

Solution matrix:
(      5,000 )
(      2,500 )

Discrepancy matrix:
(      0,000 )
(      0,000 )

